attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Unbeatable city living in the heart of vibrant South Boston! This 3rd floor spacious 1839 SF contemporary unit seamlessly blends living, dining and kitchen spaces, ideal for entertaining, and culinary enthusiasts will love the sleek European kitchen’s workspaces and the top notch Viking appliances. With 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, there is room for everyone, including the king-size luxury master suite with double vanity and a glass steam shower. Your private Roof Top Deck area offers serene outdoor retreat with city views. 1 deeded garage parking and in-unit laundry. Professional managed building with elevator, common roof deck and pet play zone. Unit freshly painted and floor repolished like NEW! Less than a mile from Seaport innovation hub, Broadway T Station(Red Line to Downtown Boston and Cambridge) and Boston Harbor Beach; Neighborhood restaurants and bars, shopping, pharmacy and grocery just a few blocks away. 10 mins to I-93 and Logan airport.
